    "parts": "Acinodendron macrostachyum is a species of flowering plant in the family Melastomataceae. Unfortunately, I do not have information on the medicinal parts of Acinodendron macrostachyum. However, I can suggest that the leaves, bark, and roots of many plants in the Melastomataceae family have been used in traditional medicine in various cultures. Research on specific plants within this family may provide insights into their medicinal properties. Further study is needed to determine the medicinal parts of Acinodendron macrostachyum.",
